Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.70,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}來 闊步前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:32.80,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}大家共同仰視的 那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.43,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就算光之窗簾 緊緊合攏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.65,0:22:38.40,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}這裡也不黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:43.54,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我已經知道 這一瞬間終將結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:47.22,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如此重要 如此重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.55,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}讓我視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:51.70,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如夢似幻的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:54.58,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}瞬間就會過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:59.71,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}這是真實發生的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:05.31,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把碎片照在夕陽下確認看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:10.22,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無法忘卻 不能忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:17.24,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一幕幕精彩回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:21.73,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無論何時都映在眼裡的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:28.07,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一個個都是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.36,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:34.26,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就這樣翩然而至
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:40.22,Lyric,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\fsp0}So bright
